  m_text: 'this is classic minesweeper.

    to flag a cell you click once and to
    open one you have to click on a flaged cell

    click on one of the cells till
    you lose or open a section of zeroes.

    the number in de cell is how many
    bombs are in a 3x3 radius with de cell in the middle.'
